  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Quantum Drive</h2>Get ready for the intensity of speed, where the streets are your playground, and speed is your ally.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707960/extras/38e422440cd31d4d61dc5f3f7ebdb3cb.poster.avif?t=1773194306\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707960/extras/38e422440cd31d4d61dc5f3f7ebdb3cb.webm?t=1773194306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707960/extras/38e422440cd31d4d61dc5f3f7ebdb3cb.mp4?t=1773194306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Vibrant Scenarios</strong>: Immerse yourself in urban and rural environments filled with stunning visual details.<br></li><li> <strong>Car Customization</strong>: Enhance your vehicle with customization options, providing a unique and exclusive experience.<br></li><li> <strong>Incredible Maneuvers</strong>: Perform perfect drifts and electrifying overtakes, competing in races against the clock.<br></li><li> <strong>Ray Tracing Compatibility</strong>: Enjoy realistic and immersive graphics with ray tracing technology.<br></li><li> <strong>Variety of Cars</strong>: Choose from 8 incredible cars, each with its own style and unique performance.<br></li><li> <strong>Time Trials</strong>: Challenge yourself in exciting races where time is your true opponent.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707960/extras/361e5ce21877c2a8719278727b6b7d28.poster.avif?t=1773194306\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707960/extras/361e5ce21877c2a8719278727b6b7d28.webm?t=1773194306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707960/extras/361e5ce21877c2a8719278727b6b7d28.mp4?t=1773194306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the Thrill of Quantum Drive</h2>Every curve offers a unique opportunity for overtaking. Victory awaits those willing to push the limits. Do you have what it takes to dominate the streets?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Development Stalled</h2>",
